1. Define a function to place an order for a product by providing a product variant ID, customer information, and shipping details:
```javascript
async function placeOrder(variantId, quantity, customer, shipping) {
  const order = {
    email: customer.email,
    fulfillment_status: "unfulfilled",
    send_receipt: true,
    send_fulfillment_receipt: true,
    line_items: [
      {
